{"lastModified":1761301221166,"uri":"c::8183534776::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Base Port: Corsica - Sardinia\nWinter Base Port: Saint Vincent - Grenadines\n\nOperating Area: \nSummer Operating Area: Riviera, Corsica, Sardinia, Mallorca, Ibiza, Menorca\nWinter Operating Area: Windward Islands (Saint Vincent, Grenadines)\n\nADEONA is a 20.36m / 67ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2021 by Fountaine Pajot. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 3. Cruising at 6.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 10.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a Master cabin and 3 VIP cabins with en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"ADEONA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::K8HYDnTPMb.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-XZm_p42MG1.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-WObkX-Swm.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-HXdaZWnhw.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-nyMxe83_y4.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-KUOUQxM1g.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-TRVPP7fUz.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::87922480-ab3a-11f0-a7b9-b1c02ec5ef0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::87938410-ab3a-11f0-a7b9-b1c02ec5ef0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fae-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100256-Uz8WnkUEZ.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4